$ON_ZACCRNDCDT
Onevent BEFORE_AREA Gosub AV_ZACCRNDCDT From W1SIPAR7
Return

$AV_ZACCRNDCDT
Call LECTEXTRA(zc,"GACCOUNT","DESTRA",num$([M:SIP5]COA),num$([M]ACCRNDCDT(indice))) From ATEXTRA
Gosub _AFF
Return

$CHG_STY
Return


